<title>Filtrera bort filer</title>

<p>När du jämför mappar, kanske du vill kunna ignorera vissa filer. Till exempel kanske du vill bara se filer som är närvarande och olika i båda mapparna, ignorerar de som är samma eller finns bara i en mapp. Alternativt , kanske du vill ignorera alla filer i din <file>.git</file> katalogen, eller ignorera alla bilder. </p>

<p>
<app>Meld</app> has several different ways of controlling which files
and what kind of differences you see. You can filter based on
<link xref="#file-state-filter">differences between a file across
folders</link> or <link xref="#file-name-filter">file and folder
names</link>. You can also tell <app>Meld</app> to treat filenames
as being <link xref="#file-case-filter">case insensitive</link>.
Finally, you can use <link xref="text-filters">text filters</link> to
change what both folder and file comparisons see.
</p>

<note style="important">
  <p>Eventuella <link xref="text-filters">textfilter</link> du har definierat <em>automatiskt gälla</em> när man jämför mappar. Filer som är identiska trots alla textfiler tillämpas inte markeras som annorlunda, men visas i kursiv stil.</p>
</note>



<section id="file-state-filter">
<title>File skillnader filtrerings</title>

<p>
In a folder comparison, each line contains a single file or folder
that is present in at least one of the folders being compared. Each of
these lines is classified as being either <em>Modifed</em>, <em>New</em>
or <em>Same</em>:
